      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STILL BELIEVE (4) last start finished 2nd on March 18 over 450m at this track behind Blanket Game beaten 2.25 lengths (25.38) in a Grade 4/5. Expected to go close with a clean break. MAXIMUM SUNSET (2) showed good early speed and led throughout to score her maiden two back then finished fourth last start and beaten 15 lengths at Warrnambool over 390m (23.34). Returns to the scene of her maiden win. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. BLACKPOOL IRIS (3) missed the frame latest but had been racing well prior to that including a Restricted WIN win two back (22.55) at Geelong. Can feature with the right run. PAW REVY (8) is always a threat when she races at this track and distance.",
